---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Nostromo-Class Commercial Towing Vehicle"
  description="The Lockmart CM-88B Bison M-Class star freighter -- Nostromo-class commercial towing vehicle. 334m length, crew of 7, MU-TH-UR 6000 OS. The backbone of interstellar commerce."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center pt-20 pb-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          FREIGHT & TRANSPORT -- VESSEL CLASS PROFILE
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-[9rem] font-black text-white mb-4 leading-none uppercase">
          NOSTROMO<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">CLASS</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-6"></div>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          LOCKMART CM-88B BISON M-CLASS STAR FREIGHTER
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vessel Data Bar -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 divide-x divide-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">CLASS</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">CM-88B BISON</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">TYPE</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">M-CLASS STAR FREIGHTER</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">MANUFACTURER</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">LOCKMART</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">CREW</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">7 STANDARD</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">STATUS</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] status-active">IN SERVICE</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
            <div>
              <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
                CLASS OVERVIEW
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8">
                THE BACKBONE OF <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">INTERSTELLAR COMMERCE</span>
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE NOSTROMO-CLASS COMMERCIAL TOWING VEHICLE IS THE WORKHORSE OF INTERSTELLAR FREIGHT OPERATIONS. MANUFACTURED BY LOCKMART AS THE CM-88B BISON M-CLASS STAR FREIGHTER, THESE VESSELS ARE DESIGNED FOR DEEP SPACE COMMERCIAL TOWING AND AUTOMATED ORE REFINERY TRANSPORT ACROSS THE LONGEST TRADE ROUTES IN THE NETWORK.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> OPERATING WITH A STANDARD CREW COMPLEMENT OF SEVEN, THE NOSTROMO-CLASS PRIORITIZES OPERATIONAL EFFICIENCY AND PAYLOAD CAPACITY OVER PASSENGER COMFORT. CREW SPEND THE MAJORITY OF TRANSIT TIME IN HYPERSLEEP, WITH THE MU-TH-UR 6000 SHIPBOARD OPERATING SYSTEM MANAGING ALL NAVIGATION, PROPULSION, AND LIFE SUPPORT FUNCTIONS AUTONOMOUSLY.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> DOZENS OF NOSTROMO-CLASS VESSELS ARE CURRENTLY IN ACTIVE SERVICE ACROSS ALL MAJOR TRADE ROUTES, HAULING ORE REFINERIES, MINERAL CARGO, CONSTRUCTION MATERIALS, AND INDUSTRIAL EQUIPMENT BETWEEN COLONY WORLDS, MINING OPERATIONS, AND EARTH-PROXIMATE PROCESSING FACILITIES.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase border-b-2 border-[#FFC600] pb-3">TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-mono">
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">DESIGNATION</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">NOSTROMO-CLASS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">MODEL</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">CM-88B BISON</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">CLASSIFICATION</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">M-CLASS STAR FREIGHTER</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">LENGTH</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">334 METERS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">WIDTH</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">215 METERS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">HEIGHT</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">98 METERS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">CREW</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">7 (STANDARD)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">OPERATING SYSTEM</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">MU-TH-UR 6000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">LIFEBOAT</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">NARCISSUS-CLASS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">MANUFACTURER</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">LOCKMART</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Deck Configuration -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            CONFIGURATION
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            VESSEL <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">LAYOUT</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">A</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">A DECK</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">BRIDGE & COMMAND</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              PRIMARY BRIDGE, NAVIGATION SYSTEMS, COMMUNICATIONS ARRAY, AND COMMAND OPERATIONS. THE MU-TH-UR 6000 MAINFRAME INTERFACE IS ACCESSIBLE FROM A DECK. ALL FLIGHT OPERATIONS AND COURSE CORRECTIONS ARE MANAGED FROM THIS LEVEL.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">B</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">B DECK</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">CREW QUARTERS & OPERATIONS</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              CREW LIVING QUARTERS, MESS HALL, MEDICAL BAY, HYPERSLEEP CHAMBERS, AND RECREATION AREAS. B DECK IS THE PRIMARY HABITATION LEVEL FOR THE SEVEN-PERSON CREW DURING WAKING PERIODS OF THE VOYAGE.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">C</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">C DECK</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">ENGINEERING & CARGO</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              MAIN ENGINEERING, FTL DRIVE ACCESS, REACTOR SYSTEMS, CARGO INTERFACE, AND TOWING MECHANISMS. C DECK HOUSES ALL PROPULSION AND POWER GENERATION SYSTEMS AND PROVIDES ACCESS TO THE EXTERNAL TOW COUPLING ARRAY.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Systems -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              SYSTEMS
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
              KEY <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">SYSTEMS</span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">MU</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">MU-TH-UR 6000</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
                THE SHIPBOARD ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE AND OPERATING SYSTEM. MU-TH-UR 6000 MANAGES ALL AUTONOMOUS NAVIGATION, FTL COURSE CALCULATIONS, LIFE SUPPORT REGULATION, HYPERSLEEP MONITORING, AND EMERGENCY PROTOCOLS. CREW INTERFACE VIA DEDICATED TERMINAL ON A DECK. THE SYSTEM OPERATES UNDER WEYLAND-YUTANI CORPORATE DIRECTIVES AT ALL TIMES.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">NC</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">NARCISSUS-CLASS LIFEBOAT</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
                EACH NOSTROMO-CLASS VESSEL CARRIES A NARCISSUS-CLASS EMERGENCY SHUTTLE. THE COMPACT LIFEBOAT PROVIDES AUTONOMOUS ESCAPE AND RESCUE CAPABILITY FOR UP TO FOUR PERSONNEL, WITH INDEPENDENT PROPULSION, LIFE SUPPORT, HYPERSLEEP, AND EMERGENCY BEACON SYSTEMS. DESIGNED FOR SYSTEM-RANGE TRANSIT TO THE NEAREST INHABITED WORLD OR TRANSIT LANE.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">HS</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">HYPERSLEEP SYSTEM</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
                SEVEN INDIVIDUAL HYPERSLEEP PODS ENABLING CREW TO ENTER CRYOGENIC SUSPENSION FOR THE DURATION OF INTERSTELLAR TRANSIT. SYSTEM MONITORED CONTINUOUSLY BY MU-TH-UR 6000. STANDARD WAKE PROTOCOL INITIATES CREW REVIVAL UPON APPROACH TO DESTINATION OR IN RESPONSE TO PRIORITY COMMUNICATIONS.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">TC</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">TOW COUPLING ARRAY</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
                THE PRIMARY COMMERCIAL FUNCTION OF THE NOSTROMO-CLASS: A HEAVY-DUTY TOW COUPLING SYSTEM RATED FOR REFINERY PLATFORMS AND CARGO ASSEMBLIES EXCEEDING 2,000,000 METRIC TONS. THE COUPLING ARRAY DISTRIBUTES FTL FIELD COVERAGE TO THE TOWED PAYLOAD, ENABLING SUPERLUMINAL TRANSIT OF MASSIVE CARGO CONFIGURATIONS.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="terminal mt-16">
            <div class="terminal-content">
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                &gt; "THE NOSTROMO-CLASS IS NOT GLAMOROUS. IT IS NOT FAST. IT IS NOT COMFORTABLE. BUT IT MOVES THE RAW MATERIALS AND PROCESSED GOODS THAT SUSTAIN EVERY COLONY IN THE NETWORK. WITHOUT THESE VESSELS, INTERSTELLAR COMMERCE WOULD CEASE AND THE COLONIAL ECONOMY WOULD COLLAPSE WITHIN A FISCAL QUARTER. THE NOSTROMO-CLASS IS THE BACKBONE OF EVERYTHING WE HAVE BUILT."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <section class="relative py-12 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/fleet" class="btn-secondary">ALL FLEET</a>
          <a href="/fleet/covenant-class" class="btn-secondary">COVENANT-CLASS</a>
          <a href="/fleet/conestoga-class" class="btn-secondary">CONESTOGA-CLASS</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
